Tharisa shareholders are referred to the announcements wherein Tharisa advised that it had acquired an option to acquire a 90% shareholding in Salene Chrome Zimbabwe at the par value thereof from Leto Settlement, a related party, published on 16 May 2018, the transaction status update announcement published on 21 August 2018 and the amended terms of the acquisition announcement published on 18 September 2018. Related: Tharisa: Developing a future in Zimbabwe Shareholders are now advised that the parties have agreed to extend the option to acquire the 90% shareholding in Salene Chrome to 31 March 2021.